Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.62,0:02:27.50,lassie episode,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:142622,147502}{\blur0.5\fad(300,0)\pos(320,295)}Welcome Back, Lassie
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.32,0:02:33.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:152320,153240}John,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.89,0:02:36.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:153890,156610}There is no news of Lassie for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.17,0:02:41.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:157170,161970}Its last appearance was\Nthree days ago of West Darlington.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.55,0:02:48.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:162550,168050}But I'm sure Lasie has traveled safely and\Nit will arrive soon, that's what I think!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.79,0:02:51.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:169790,171740}Don't worry, Priscilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.94,0:02:56.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:171940,176520}Lassie is in good health and is\Non its way to… my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.41,0:03:18.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:193410,198180}I thought of Lassie until the morning came…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.89,0:03:35.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:213890,215750}It is the result of the geological survey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.75,0:03:38.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:215750,218660}If the result is zero,\NI can't assume that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.79,0:03:39.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:218790,219430}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.70,0:03:42.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:219700,222590}Let's do our best and find coal, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.63,0:03:49.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:223630,229830}When I see these two working, I feel\Nthat the coal will definitely come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.25,0:03:50.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:230250,230940}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.17,0:03:54.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:231170,234210}Well, we too will not lose\Nto the current manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:55.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:234330,235440}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:06.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:245470,246680}Ah Sandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.34,0:04:08.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:247340,248400}How is your health?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.44,0:04:10.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:249440,250180}Hm…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.82,0:04:13.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:250820,253170}There is no escape from that as you see…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.37,0:04:15.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:253370,255040}What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.16,0:04:16.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:255160,256430}This is your gift!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:17.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:256650,257290}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:19.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:258400,259540}Thank you…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.53,0:04:23.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:260530,263350}I… why I'm always so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.44,0:04:26.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:263440,266190}And to get sick at such an important time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.58,0:04:28.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:266580,268080}I feel embarrassed by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.23,0:04:30.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:268230,270410}I can't help John at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.64,0:04:31.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:270640,271610}Maybe so!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.71,0:04:33.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:271710,273910}So the same with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.33,0:04:39.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:274330,279750}All I can do is make tea at their own leisure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.05,0:04:40.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:280050,280790}Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.03,0:04:45.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:281030,285970}John is doing hard work like a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.28,0:04:46.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:286280,286940}Ah…!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.00,0:04:52.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:287000,292100}But when everyone treats the candy they offer\Nthem will increase their strength as I think!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:53.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:292600,293630}Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:55.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:294770,295740}John…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.84,0:04:59.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:295840,299360}Actually wants to find Lassie but he can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.70,0:05:03.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:299700,303750}That's why he desperately tries\Nto find coal with others.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.46,0:05:07.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:304460,307990}When Lassie returns,\Nthey will always live together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.43,0:05:10.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:309430,310300}Hm…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.07,0:05:15.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:311070,315870}I hope Lassie returns while he is in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.72,0:05:21.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:316720,321460}When I see it in good health,\NI expect to stay next to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.90,0:05:22.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:321900,322750}Hm…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.97,0:05:25.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:322970,325540}I wish I could do even a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.04,0:05:26.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:326040,326790}Ah…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.89,0:05:28.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:326890,328230}You can't…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.89,0:05:35.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:333890,335410}And now everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.54,0:05:37.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:335540,337100}Time for tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.36,0:05:39.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:337360,339470}Oh? What is our food today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.69,0:05:42.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:339690,342310}The meat pie is full of energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.47,0:05:45.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:342470,345450}Every day I look forward to this moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.54,0:05:46.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:345540,346860}Well, take a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.86,0:05:58.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:357860,358770}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:01.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:359380,361250}Yes! Thank you for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.47,0:06:06.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:364470,366650}W-what, did you eat already?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:14.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:373310,374190}John!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.48,0:06:15.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:374480,375220}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:17.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:375560,377810}I don't help much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.89,0:06:20.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:378890,380420}Don't help too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.16,0:06:22.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:381160,382780}You do everything you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:24.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:383630,384370}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:26.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:385690,386870}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.67,0:06:29.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:387670,389280}Ah, one week only?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.48,0:06:30.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:389480,390200}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.58,0:06:31.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:390580,391940}It is time to hold your breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.97,0:06:34.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:391970,394440}Wellington Coal Mine has reached its limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.55,0:06:38.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:394550,398090}The bank is no longer able\Nto pay costs without interest!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:41.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:399000,401210}Now we can't extract coal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.36,0:06:42.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:401360,402900}Maybe we should give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.99,0:06:45.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:402990,405000}But, just a week!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.08,0:06:45.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:405080,405910}Sam…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.60,0:06:49.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:406600,409960}I have to tell everyone the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.33,0:06:53.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:410330,413290}We need to think about\Nthe future of our new life!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.95,0:06:58.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:416950,418700}We should talk to John.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.38,0:07:02.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:420380,422580}Do you have the power to tell him directly?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.38,0:07:05.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:423380,425480}I'm not sure I can say it…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.12,0:07:08.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:426120,428130}No, I'm going to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.90,0:07:10.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:428900,430670}I think you understand that too…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.92,0:07:14.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:430920,434240}John has recently become more mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.36,0:07:15.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:434360,435690}I wish that he was…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:23.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:440330,443400}What is the matter with the manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.80,0:07:26.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:443800,446420}He seems to be talking\Nabout something different.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:29.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:446690,449370}I hope to not say to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.49,0:07:32.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:451490,452780}Hey he's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.13,0:07:33.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:453130,453870}Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.25,0:07:36.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:455250,456790}Listen everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.87,0:07:38.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:456870,458360}The manager has something to tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.54,0:07:54.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:473540,474270}You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.39,0:07:56.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:474390,476340}Is it a unique stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.49,0:07:58.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:476490,478390}I have extracted it from the wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.76,0:07:59.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:478760,479660}Sandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.01,0:08:01.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:480010,481790}This! Probably…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:04.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:482460,484270}Just a moment, bring that book to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.41,0:08:05.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:484410,485840}- The yellow one!\N- Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:06.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:486400,486970}Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:08.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:487000,488760}Wait for me to sort them out first!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.23,0:08:09.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:489230,489930}This one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.03,0:08:12.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:490030,492930}No… that one! The third one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.07,0:08:14.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:493070,494040}Right! That one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.44,0:08:15.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:494440,495190}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.33,0:08:17.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:496330,497090}Hm…!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:19.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:498390,499310}What is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:21.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:500720,501650}There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:23.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:501680,503640}There it is! Ammonite!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.82,0:08:24.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:503820,504510}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.93,0:08:25.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:504930,505630}Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.66,0:08:26.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:505660,506980}This is serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.43,0:08:28.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:507430,508410}What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.43,0:08:30.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:508430,510010}That's serious, Sandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:30.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:510150,510920}Hm…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.33,0:08:35.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:514330,515650}What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.97,0:08:39.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:516970,519500}Manager, tell us quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.52,0:08:42.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:519520,522170}We are also about to lose our temper!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.52,0:08:49.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:526520,529300}Manager, should I say that instead of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.12,0:08:51.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:530120,531000}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.31,0:08:52.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:531310,532930}I can't say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.21,0:08:59.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:538210,539110}Everyone…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.58,0:09:00.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:539580,540440}No…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:01.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:540720,541610}I mean…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.88,0:09:02.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:541880,542920}Somewhat…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.32,0:09:05.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:544320,545710}No, I mean…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:08.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:546150,548340}We have to let you all know…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.42,0:09:10.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:548420,550100}Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.28,0:09:13.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:550280,553060}Hey sir! It's serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.10,0:09:14.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:553100,554350}Serious thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.39,0:09:15.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554390,555020}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.01,0:09:19.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:557010,559280}What is the matter? Why you were running?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.43,0:09:20.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:559430,560750}In fact…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.61,0:09:24.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:563610,564830}What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.46,0:09:34.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:573460,574300}This…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.33,0:09:35.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:574330,575120}Oh…!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.27,0:09:38.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:575270,578880}There it is! It's a carbon\Nelement of antiquity!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.27,0:09:40.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:579270,580540}It is an Ammonite…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.19,0:09:42.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:581190,582360}This means…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:44.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:582990,584030}What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.55,0:09:48.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:584550,588640}Coal is a tree grown in the\Nearth since ancient times!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.99,0:09:50.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:588990,590880}But this oyster…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.90,0:09:51.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:590900,591910}This is not an object!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.01,0:09:55.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:592010,595440}Ah… sir, it is a bit different…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.87,0:09:56.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:595870,596580}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.67,0:09:59.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:597670,599450}In any case, we have to determine
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.47,0:10:01.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:599470,601710}the age of this object and it will\Ncertainly determine the age of the tree
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:03.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:601780,603510}that has grown since ancient times\Nand is the main source of coal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:05.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:603540,605840}The object indicates\Nthe presence of coal as well…!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.84,0:10:07.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:605840,607790}Yeah, and charcoal too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:10.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:608670,610900}Well, we have to dig more!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.93,0:10:14.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:610930,614150}We don't know what is coming\Nout to us, but let's dig, let's dig!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.18,0:10:15.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:614180,615110}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.18,0:10:16.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:615180,616640}Ah, Colin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.64,0:10:18.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:616640,618340}Hey, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:19.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:618430,619770}Thank you, Colin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:20.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:619950,620990}No way…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:23.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:621140,623400}Sandy is the one who\Npicked it up from the mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.51,0:10:25.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:623510,625880}I thought it was a plain stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:27.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:626100,627700}Be proud of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.91,0:10:40.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:637910,640210}Hey! Something else appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.36,0:10:41.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:640360,641370}Is it coal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.54,0:10:43.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:641540,643860}No, but it stirred up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.06,0:10:45.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:644060,645280}Traces, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.60,0:10:46.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:645600,646890}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:48.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:646950,648640}It looks huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.65,0:10:56.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:654650,656230}Professor, how was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.58,0:10:58.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:656580,658530}It's good to find the entire body of Ariophus,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.56,0:11:03.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:658560,663450}which is considered one of\Nthe most important ancient relics!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:06.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:663800,666950}I heard that the mine will close today!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.97,0:11:09.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:666970,669440}After that I can say that coal can go out
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:12.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:669480,672120}according to previous geological studies,\Nbut still little possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.12,0:11:16.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:672120,676930}And order to close the mine,\Nit's completely wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.95,0:11:21.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:676950,681410}So I have to tell the Duke\Nto abandon his decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.43,0:11:23.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:681430,683200}That's all, sorry I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.57,0:11:25.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:683570,685280}Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:26.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:685410,686230}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.51,0:11:29.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:686510,689190}You thank the children!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.22,0:11:29.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:689220,689950}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.24,0:11:32.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:690240,692200}What? What about John?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:35.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:692350,695200}He's in the place I found the oyster,\Nand digs with Mr. Pia and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:36.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:695590,696950}I'ts enough…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.07,0:11:39.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:697070,699590}He wants to continue until the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.27,0:11:46.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:705270,706050}John!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.24,0:11:46.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:706240,706860}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.01,0:11:47.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:707010,707980}You have to stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.23,0:11:49.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:708230,709820}Leave the rest to your father!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.92,0:11:50.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:709920,710750}Yes, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.75,0:11:52.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:710750,712520}John, come here a little bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.88,0:11:54.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:712880,714540}What's up, Mr. Pia?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.76,0:11:56.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:715760,716800}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.36,0:12:05.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:723360,725370}We have finally done it, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.02,0:12:09.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:728020,729960}We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.96,0:12:11.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:729960,731630}We finally did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.63,0:12:13.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:731630,733670}Coal has come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.46,0:12:28.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:747460,748300}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.06,0:12:45.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:764060,765540}Well done, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.64,0:12:49.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:765640,769770}With this thing Lassie\Ncan come back to me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.02,0:12:50.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:770020,770740}John…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.55,0:12:55.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:771550,775690}After feeling comfortable I feel sleepy…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.04,0:12:59.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:776040,779870}I'm glad I trusted you, Dad…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.62,0:13:03.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:780620,783020}I… somehow…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.66,0:13:05.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:783660,785440}Sleepy…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.71,0:13:07.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:785710,787050}Lassie…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.99,0:13:09.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:788990,789730}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.86,0:13:11.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:790860,791770}John…
Comment: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:15.02,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:795024,795024}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.09,0:13:22.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:799090,802870}He felt relieved after he was nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.65,0:13:28.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:805650,808060}So let him sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.23,0:13:30.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:809230,810870}What about Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.21,0:13:35.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:811210,815380}I have received a message from\NPriscilla but there is no news of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.45,0:13:36.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:815450,816530}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.21,0:13:44.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:823210,824400}Lassie…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.51,0:13:52.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:830510,832600}Wait, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.81,0:13:58.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:837810,838650}Lassie…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.67,0:14:00.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:838670,840840}So we can always stay together!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.27,0:14:04.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:843270,844340}Together…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.98,0:14:08.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:844980,848880}Lassie is no longer on my side!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.14,0:14:12.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:850140,852610}I wonder if it is still walking?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.46,0:14:16.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:853460,856580}But, where does it walk in this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.44,0:14:21.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:860440,861330}Lassie…!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.70,0:14:25.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:862700,865010}Where did you go, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.61,0:14:30.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:868610,870470}Oh! Where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:33.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:871430,873260}Where do you walk now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.80,0:14:43.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:882800,883830}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.13,0:14:54.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:893130,894300}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.64,0:15:01.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:899640,901940}Lassie… I'm sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.32,0:15:04.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:902320,904000}I've made you tire a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.62,0:15:11.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:910620,911480}John?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.06,0:15:13.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:912060,913220}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.05,0:15:17.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:917050,917890}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.59,0:15:21.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:920590,921740}Priscilla?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.65,0:15:25.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:923650,925000}Did you sleep well?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.67,0:15:29.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:925670,929200}They came from Scotland by plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.97,0:15:31.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:929970,931520}By plane!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.81,0:15:33.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:931810,933630}Did I sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.72,0:15:34.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:933720,934890}For two days!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.19,0:15:35.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:935190,935990}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.44,0:15:38.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:936440,938740}Have I really slept all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.09,0:15:40.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:939090,940300}John!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.93,0:15:43.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:941930,943150}Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.24,0:15:44.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:943240,944540}Because of your faith,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.70,0:15:48.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:944700,948990}you brought the coal out again,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.11,0:15:50.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:949110,950450}though I didn't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:51.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:950550,951480}Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.65,0:15:53.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:951650,953340}You've done a really good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.37,0:15:56.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:953370,956740}Your heart has won over me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.15,0:15:58.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:957150,958100}However…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.55,0:16:00.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:959550,960770}I apologise…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.33,0:16:05.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:961330,965050}I promised you that I would give Lassie back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.11,0:16:07.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:965110,967410}But I couldn't keep it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.74,0:16:10.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:967740,970330}You are the only one who\Ncan take care of Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.36,0:16:11.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:970360,971920}Right, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.01,0:16:13.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:972010,973900}I have to find Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.44,0:16:18.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:975440,978120}Lassie is still walking towards our village!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.26,0:16:18.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:978260,978860}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.15,0:16:21.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:979150,981330}Get out! My clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.36,0:16:23.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:981360,983360}- John!\N- You'll change your clothes, John?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:26.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:984960,986720}Listen, John
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.82,0:16:30.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:986820,990660}If Lassie returns,\Nit will be like a miracle!
